174
00:12:36,445 --> 00:12:37,993
Som rada, že to vieš.

175
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:39,595
Si si istý, že si sa celkom uzdravil?

176
00:12:40,117 --> 00:12:41,999
Ak mi neveríš,

177
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,532
